        <dialogReference>&lt;p&gt;Add Point Order&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Boolean&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Default: 0&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Add point order as additional attribute.&lt;/p&gt;</dialogReference>
